description: Colorectal adenomas are cancer precursor lesions of the large bowel. In these preinvasive lesions, a vast array of genomic and epigenomic changes have been detailed, but the consequence of these molecular alterations on the effectors of biological function (proteins) has not been comprehensively explored.
